  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to compare the safety and efficacy of a tacrolimus-based 5-day
      steroid rapid withdrawal immunoprophylactic regimen in de novo renal transplantation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
